# Optional: point Jetty at the RTSP helper HTTP API (default: use Vite dev proxy paths /jetty-live-stream).
# Local dev: start the helper with `npm run dev:stream` or `npm run dev:jetty-live` from repo root (see Docs/Plan/LOCAL-DEV.md).
# Example direct URL:
# VITE_JETTY_LIVE_HTTP_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:3080
#
# Optional WebSocket port when using direct origin (health JSON may override).
# VITE_JETTY_LIVE_WS_PORT=9999
#
# Beta: Vessel Pipeline — Actuals widget on Dashboard (staging opt-in; rebuild required).
# VITE_ENABLE_PIPELINE_ACTUALS_BETA=true
